    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You fire off a volley of energy palings with your Innocence (Cross). Make 2 ranged taijutsu attacks against any creatures in range dealing your weapons damage +1d6 and for every two hits you land with this jutsu on a single creature they gain 1 rank of bleed.<br />If this jutsu is cast as a Chain 2, the additional damage dice become d8s. If this jutsu is cast as a Chain 3 the target instead gains one rank of bleed per hit.<br />At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the number of attacks by +1. If this jutsu is cast at A-Rank the damage increases by +1 dice.</p>",
